name: Galaxy Flame
author: Rhoq
description:
Made
 this for the "Let the Galaxy Burn" event (though I did not finish my 
wip in time). Warm tones for distant galactic gas clouds, flames and 
stars, and the cool tones for skies, spaceships, and other 
science-fictional constructs. Semi-saturated darks in red, blue, and 
green to keep some life in the deep places.
